257
00:14:39,529 --> 00:14:43,002
"Questa storia e' finita, e
Dio salvi tutta la compagnia."

258
00:14:47,730 --> 00:14:49,364
Che diavolo era?

259
00:14:50,172 --> 00:14:52,584
